{"tid":1873283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"RV全員為動畫《魔髮精靈》續集配音 官方海報公開還原可愛本色","createTime":"2020-02-10T14:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T15:02:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5dfaefa0bef40f109b8ef74c110a256c3123c1","tid":1873283,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/02/20200210_EN_RevVelvetTrolls_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F02%2F20200210_EN_RevVelvetTrolls_FB.jpg&h=424085c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n角色名同頭髮顏色都襯返5位成員！<br />\n<br />\n由美國動畫公司夢工場製作的3D動畫音樂電影《魔髮精靈》（Trolls)於2016年首度上映，原版由Anna Kendrick和Justin Timberlake聲演主角，戲中可愛角色和多首原聲帶OST也深受觀眾和樂迷喜愛。而即將在今年4月份上映的續集&mdash;《魔髮精靈：唱遊大世界》（Trolls: World Tour）中，Red Velvet（RV）的5位成員也確定加入原聲班底，將以配音和演唱形式參與聲演戲中的「K-POP Trolls」與全世界的觀眾們見面。<br />\n<br />\nRed Velvet 9日晚在官方社交網站上分享了5位成員參與《魔髮精靈：唱遊大世界》的角色海報，Irene聲演粉紅色頭髮的「Baby Bun」、Seulgi是黃色的「Gomdori」、Wendy是藍髮的「Wani」、Joy是綠色的「Ari」，還有Yeri是紫色的「Kim-Petit」。小精靈版的的RV不止角色名字和造型可愛，連頭髮顏色也是5位成員各自的代表顏色，可謂是「度身訂做」的角色。<br />\n<br />\n該動畫片的製作人表示：「Red Velvet在追求多種音樂風格的同時，也給全世界的音樂粉絲們帶來了獨一無二的魅力，選組合作為K-POP的代表卡士，亦是卓越的選擇。在一起錄音的過程中，成員們不僅展現了各自的個性，還完美地融入了『K-POP TROLLS』角色中，讓人不禁期待Red Velvet的活躍。」此前《魔髮精靈：唱遊大世界》公開的官方動畫預告中，可聽到Red Velvet的歌曲《Zimzalabim》在背景中出現，還有RV成員講英文對白，均令粉絲們表示興奮和相當期待。電影預計4月於全球陸續上畫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5883362-rv%E5%85%A8%E5%93%A1%E7%82%BA%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E3%80%8A%E9%AD%94%E9%AB%AE%E7%B2%BE%E9%9D%88%E3%80%8B%E7%BA%8C%E9%9B%86%E9%85%8D%E9%9F%B3-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B?current_cat=119360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5883362-rv%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2595%25AB%25E3%2580%258A%25E9%25AD%2594%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%259D%2588%25E3%2580%258B%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%2585%258D%25E9%259F%25B3-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%3Fcurrent_cat%3D119360&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4Yc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=ad7ed93a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5883362-rv%E5%85%A8%E5%93%A1%E7%82%BA%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E3%80%8A%E9%AD%94%E9%AB%AE%E7%B2%BE%E9%9D%88%E3%80%8B%E7%BA%8C%E9%9B%86%E9%85%8D%E9%9F%B3-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B?current_cat=119360</a>"},{"pid":"37bd5225cec7b1993a6f9ce9a635e0d01453f57f","tid":1873283,"uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"期待喔❤️❤️❤️❤️<br />\n準備去韓國日日睇呢套野了"},{"pid":"f0777cb7a838b3d3fa640f908ba668189128a195","tid":1873283,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"Seulgi❤️"},{"pid":"27c3608e7c100f87bfa05adba0a60586918a2767","tid":1873283,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0777cb7a838b3d3fa640f908ba668189128a195","tid":1873283,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"Seulgi❤️"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:58:11.000Z","msg":"Happy Birthday ❤️❤️❤️"},{"pid":"97d0dc6b498cf87a10e661a01a7a248362fa75fc","tid":1873283,"uid":48577,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27c3608e7c100f87bfa05adba0a60586918a2767","tid":1873283,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0777cb7a838b3d3fa640f908ba668189128a195","tid":1873283,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"Seulgi❤️"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:58:11.000Z","msg":"Happy Birthday ❤️❤️❤️"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0L7p3S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0L7p3S.gif&h=f06b6867&s={SI